{{Scripting}}[http://groovy.codehaus.org/ Groovy] is an agile and dynamic language for the Java Virtual Machine. It builds upon the strengths of [[Java]] but has additional power features inspired by languages like [[Python]], [[Ruby]] and Smalltalk.

= Quickstart =

* Press {{key|[}} to bring up the [[Script Editor]].
* Select an example Groovy script from the <code>Templates > Groovy</code> menu.
* Press {{key|Ctrl}}+{{key|R}} to run the script!

